nodes.text: 200 Reasons Why We Love Star Wars

200 Reasons Why We Love Star Wars is an article featured in Star Wars Insider 200. Published February 9, 2021, it celebrates two-hundred issues of Star Wars Insider with two-hundred reasons to love Star Wars from various people who have contributed to Star Wars over the years. It mistakenly says that Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens was released in 1999 as opposed to 2015.
